      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, goblin tax? i dont get it. are you saying there are literal fees i'm not seeing? i need to understand the actual math. can you just explain the formula for the monthly interest calculation without the metaphors? i'm trying to figure out if my bank is actually calculating it right.",
